    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#mohamed-jmr-cdl2007"/>, pp. 35-37, n. <citedRange>3</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>57.2005</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>108500</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, p. <citedRange>125</citedRange> (findspot), pp. <citedRange>196-197</citedRange> (typology), pp. <citedRange>374-375</citedRange>, number 101 (text)</bibl>.</p>
              </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
